  "body": "# Issue Design Review\r\n\r\nDesign review for the community components in Quo 2 Library:\r\n\r\n**- Community Card View:** the permission tag design needs to be updated as well as the active members icon. Card looks too wide compared to design _(need more option to display description, stats and tags to check the spacing between the elements)_\r\n**- Discover card:** the illustration is missing and the corners are too rounded\r\n**- Token gating:** loading icon is bigger compared to the others, they should keep the same size (see add state compared to hodl state icon size)\r\n\r\n## Figma frame\r\n\r\nHere's the [Figma frame](https://www.figma.com/file/Tf5nfkYvpbnNCo4rKLK7lS/Feedback-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=3374%3A287556&mode=design&t=UAAEFaABoJ5a0AvU-1) with comments and DS components.\r\n\r\n## Screenshots\r\n\r\nCommunity Card View:\r\n<img width=\"463\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-13 alle 14 26 31\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/122543089/b939380e-9e51-43c7-ad1a-656eb7da6bb9\">\r\n\r\nDiscover Card:\r\n<img width=\"510\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-13 alle 14 26 52\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/122543089/c02fb812-e7ac-4302-9660-fa7cd5b7515f\">\r\n\r\nToken gating:\r\n<img width=\"585\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-07-13 alle 14 27 19\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/122543089/5cdbe5aa-3e83-4a71-949c-893004c829f6\">\r\n",
